# Locked Stack

This project uses a fixed technology stack. No agent may deviate from these choices without explicit user instruction.

| Concern | Choice | Prohibited alternatives |
|---|---|---|
| Framework | React 18 via Vite | Next.js, Remix, SvelteKit, Vue, Angular |
| Language | JavaScript / JSX | TypeScript, TSX |
| Styling | Plain CSS / CSS Modules | Tailwind, Sass, Less, styled-components, Emotion, CSS-in-JS of any kind |
| State | React Context + useReducer | Redux, Zustand, Jotai, MobX |
| Data | Static JSON files | REST API calls, GraphQL, server-side rendering |
| Build | Vite | webpack, Parcel, esbuild standalone |
| Target browsers | Chrome 109+ / Firefox ESR 115+ | IE, Safari-only features |
| Target resolution | 1280×720 minimum | Mobile-first breakpoints |

Never install a new npm dependency without explicit user approval. Never introduce TypeScript, a CSS preprocessor, or a state management library. Never replace CSS Modules with any CSS-in-JS approach.

